HEADWORD: Mollusk
<hw>Mol"lusk</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>mollusque</ets>, L. <ets>mollusca</ets> a kind of soft nut with a
thin shell, fr. <ets>molluscus</ets> soft, <ets>mollis</ets> soft. See
<er>Mollify</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>One of the
<phylum>Mollusca</phylum>.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>mollusc</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

